{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_7_level_main_07-04_end","storyGroup":"main_7","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"main_7_level_main_07-03_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"7-5","storyName":"并肩之约-2","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"经历了一系列波折后，博士、阿米娅以及其他干员最终顺利登上了切尔诺伯格核心城。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_07-04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_07-04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["凯尔希","阿米娅","煌","迷迭香","工程干员","罗德岛干员","临光","守林人","极境","杜宾","驾驶员"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Character","id":4},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"Dialog","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"Text","text":"6:00am","id":7},{"type":"Dialog","id":8},{"type":"Character","id":9},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"coverall","id":11},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$frontline_intro","key":"$frontline_loop","volume":"0.4","id":13,"musicid":0},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"15","text":"消灭侦查部队后，不会剩多少时间。"}],"values":[],"id":14},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":15},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"正如你所说。时间紧迫。","id":17,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"19","text":"干员不会站在沙地上扒城上去。"}],"values":[],"id":18},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":19},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"呃......有些时候我们是会这么做啦。","id":21,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但是核心城正在移动中，要想进入下层基础结构，确实不容易。","id":22,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果干员站在沙地上等着移动城邦驶过，无论是相对速度还是相对高度，都限制了干员的行动。","id":24,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"没办法打开移动城邦底部的维修窗口与废料出口的话，准备好的诱饵与隐蔽会失去意义。","id":25,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"所以，我们的五支小队会通过载具，以沙尘作为掩护接近核心城，最后利用工具登上核心城的底层工业结构。","id":26,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"28","text":"罗德岛居然只派遣了五支小队？ "}],"values":[],"id":27},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":28},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们没有急着想让乌萨斯的地方将领捏到我们把柄的意思。","id":30,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"更不希望他们派出一艘高速军舰，在荒原上摧毁我们的船舰，杀死我们的雇员。","id":31,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"即使事情这么发生了，你也不会在任何一张报纸上看见证据。银行家和保险业只会划去你的名字，将所有的积累全部放进自己的保险库。","id":32,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"没有人会开口，因为乌萨斯不会希望有人开口。","id":33,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"中立身份意味着我们在夹缝中依然拥有些许的自由，相应的，罗德岛不能拥有任何政治势力作为后盾。","id":34,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"隐蔽行事是我们的生存理念。派遣小队去救你时，也是一样。","id":35,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"五支小队。留下痕迹、清除痕迹；目标完成、目标失败。无论如何，罗德岛最多只能派出五支小队。","id":36,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"38","text":"但更多小队意味着更多的武装力量！"},{"id":"38","text":"......"},{"id":"38","text":"即使没办法解决问题？"}],"values":[],"id":37},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":38},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"","id":40,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"即使是龙门这样的城邦，想要消灭我们也是易如反掌。","id":41,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你也看见了，成建制的近卫局和比起各国顶级精英武装也毫不逊色的特殊部队，他们的实力远不是一家医药公司能比的。","id":42,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"44","text":"那为什么我们要参与？ "}],"values":[],"id":43},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":44},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"因为这个阴谋已经卷入了感染者。","id":46,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"现在，罗德岛已经离开了龙门，以每小时十五公里的速度驶向下一个贸易城邦。","id":47,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在这之前，我们可能会在荒野上停留数个星期。","id":48,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"除了靠近我们的罗德岛通讯专员和可信任船只，没有人会收到我们的信号，我们会在各城邦的移动规划中，挑选出避开所有人的路线。","id":49,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"即使龙门在事件过后反悔，他们也没法再找到我们。","id":50,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"52","text":"但这样还不够吧？"}],"values":[],"id":51},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":52},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"54","text":"这一拳打上去不够狠！"},{"id":"54","text":"还要更锋利。"},{"id":"54","text":"我们的赌注应该不会只有这点。"}],"values":[],"id":53},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":54},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"没错。我们还需要额外的致命砝码。","id":56,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":58,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士和凯尔希，都变得很阴沉可怕。","id":59,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"就算我知道事情的必要性，你们也不用......露出那种笑容吧？","id":60,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿米娅......我笑了吗？","id":62,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我知道凯尔希医生笑了啦。虽然你嘴唇不动，但我是能感受到笑的。","id":64,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"竟然是这样。","id":66,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......真好！","id":68,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不，事先声明，我没有要和这个人修缮人际关系的意思。","id":70,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"72","text":"呵，我也没这个意思。"},{"id":"72","text":"......"},{"id":"72","text":"有无必要取决于双方的自由意愿。"}],"values":[],"id":71},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":72},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#6","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"欸......","id":74,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这五支小队，将分别由我、阿米娅与另外三位精英干员带领。","id":76,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"三支作战小队，一支侦察小队，以及一支特殊作业小队。","id":77,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"其中，有一支作战小队的队长，你也许该先见她一面。","id":78,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":79},{"type":"Dialog","id":80},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":81},{"type":"Character","id":82},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":83},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_bridge","screenadapt":"coverall","id":84},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"迷迭香！等等！","id":87,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.4","id":88,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"啊......煌。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"你伤得好重，怎么还跑出来？快回去。快点回去。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#9","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"你这次要出战？","id":93,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#9"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#9","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"嗯。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"我找人替你。让Misery去。他比你擅长攻坚战。","id":97,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"他一挥手就能解决的事，让他去。","id":98,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"你不想我去？","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"对，你不该去。","id":102,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"煌让人感觉很奇怪。","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"这和你以前的任务可不一样！","id":106,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"因为可能会死？","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#6","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"说啥啊！","id":110,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"你怎么能，怎么......是怎么这么轻松地说出来啊！","id":111,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"你年纪太小了，这么危险的任务，你是不该去的！","id":112,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#6","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"可阿米娅也要去。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"因为她......！她是......！","id":116,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"她是......","id":117,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"阿米娅......","id":118,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"她和我一样，是感染者，也是干员。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"而且，我检查了日志。Ace和Scout都在切尔诺伯格，他们没回来。","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"也就是说，他们已经不在了吧。","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我想去看看。我要明白是怎么回事。我要看看管整合运动的人，我要知道是谁做了什么。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我要知道在Ace和Scout身上发生了什么。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#10","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"迷迭香？这种事你......你可以不记的。","id":126,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#10"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#10","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"......煌？","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"(粗口)，我他妈在说什么......","id":130,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"不，对不起，我不该这么说。我不应该。**，我这张臭嘴！","id":131,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"可是，他们的死......他们......","id":132,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"煌。","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"错的是我。开心是记忆，伤心也是记忆。我的错。你不能不记。","id":136,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"煌变得很奇怪。说的话也支离破碎的。","id":138,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"......我不想你那么痛苦。为什么非要去回头看它？如果是你的话......是可以把记忆放走的啊。","id":140,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"你可以把它就放在那里。让它就躺在那里，不要回头。","id":141,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"如果不看......记忆又能用来做什么呢？","id":143,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"不看的话......就是忘记。","id":144,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我不会去忘掉的。我绝对不会忘记任何一个人的死。","id":145,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"哈。对。你和我一样。你也是罗德岛的精英干员。","id":147,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"不能代你去，真的，我......","id":148,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"唔，呃......","id":149,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"你又流血了？","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"小事。","id":153,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我送你。","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"哎哟。","id":157,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"煌","text":"迷迭香......和阿米娅要好好的。","id":158,"figure":"char_017_homura_3#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"嗯。我会的。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_042"},{"type":"Dialog","id":161},{"type":"Character","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":164},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"coverall","id":165},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"168","text":"很有必要吗？见她一面......？"}],"values":[],"id":167},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":168},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"Dr.{@nickname}......","id":170,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"罗德岛雇佣的精英干员们，都因为种种原因，将自身的精力和专业才能奉献给了罗德岛。","id":171,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"他们带领的小队会全心全意地支持他们的工作，因为精英干员在某些程度上，可以直接决定一种战术的运用方式。","id":172,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但他们并不都......符合我们的想象。","id":173,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"精英干员煌，博士你是见过的。有关煌的很多传闻，可能博士都没听过，实际上，被干员们添油加醋得有些厉害。","id":174,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但现在这一位精英干员，所有人对她的印象都不一样。","id":175,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"如果是博士，应该是能......慢慢地理解她和她的选择的。","id":176,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——","id":178,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"看你的反应，也许你已经见过了。","id":179,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"啊？呜......","id":181,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那......那这样就可以了吗？","id":182,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"184","text":"还有什么需要注意的？"}],"values":[],"id":183},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":184},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"大致的安排就是这样。事实上，唔......很现实的，计划是计划，行动是行动。","id":186,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"只有行动才是重要的。计划只是行动的雏形，而行动中的意外事件会打破一切计划。","id":188,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"190","text":"希望我们没人专做很糟糕的预言。"}],"values":[],"id":189},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":190},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":191},{"type":"Character","id":192},{"type":"Dialog","id":193},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"coverall","id":195},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":196},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"$exciting_loop","volume":"0.4","id":197,"musicid":2},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"糟糕.......很糟糕！有些不对！","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"......沙尘的密度还是很稀疏，现在光线的角度，不大行！","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"我们没在阴影里！如果从舰桥观察下来，我们可能会在开始全力运作前就完全暴露啦！！","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_016_medic","focus":"2","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"但已经不能再给机器添加外部遮蔽物了，一旦影响防尘器的空气流通，产生的上升气流，可能不足以保证沙尘浮动！","id":203,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_016_medic","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"怎么办，要把位置继续后移吗......？可能会赶不及！","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","id":206},{"type":"Dialog","id":207},{"type":"Character","name":"char_148_nearl_1#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......请交给我。","id":210,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"守林人，请监测实际效果，告诉我接下来要调整的方向。","id":211,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"骑士？你要......做什么？","id":213,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_148_nearl_1#3","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"改变光线的角度。","id":215,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"如果是为了减少这片大地上的苦难......我相信，连太阳的光芒，也愿意为我一时颔首。","id":216,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":217},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.5","Delay":"0.4","id":218},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.2","Delay":"0.7","id":219},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"Character","id":221},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"Character","name":"char_401_elysm","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":223},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"嗯？沙丘那边是谁？临光吗？她们不登车的还不撤退吗？","id":225,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"她在干什么呢，沉思？摆造型......在这摆造型？","id":226,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"......等等，好亮，她整个人开始发光了欸......不，等，糟了！太刺眼了！","id":227,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Character","id":228},{"type":"Dialog","id":229},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"Character","name":"char_401_elysm","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"啊，谢谢队长......","id":232,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"如果队长你的手指不是要把我的脑袋捏裂一样扒得那么紧的话，我会很感激你挡住了我的眼睛的。","id":233,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"临光在做什么啊？","id":234,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"临光没问题？可......就算队长你这么说，这光也比阳光澈烈太多了，她要干什么啊？","id":235,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialog","id":236},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.8","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":238},{"type":"Character","name":"char_401_elysm","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"嗯？怎么会......周边的光芒好像被临光渐渐同化了？","id":240,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"......呼啊。","id":241,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"队长，整个区域内的光，已经慢慢调谐成同一种感觉了。","id":242,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"我知道啊，我知道啦。我就是想说，你看，除了耀骑士，有谁能做到这种事呢？","id":243,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"队长，看看沙丘影子的投向，你猜现在是下午，还是上午？","id":244,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"唉，我......就是活跃下气氛。而且一会儿开始刮起沙尘，可就看不到影子咯？","id":245,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"我这就闭嘴。不好意思。","id":246,"figure":"char_401_elysm"},{"type":"Character","id":247},{"type":"Dialog","id":248},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_aircraft","screenadapt":"coverall","id":250},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"再高些！已经有奇怪颜色的球体划过机身了！","id":253,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"1","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"教官，别怕，整合运动的术师没有击毁我们的本事。","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"2","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"我们只是做诱饵，不是要给整合运动表演飞行技术！","id":257,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"......如果我们做得很好的话，整合运动的人也会心悦诚服地投降吧？","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"那个叫什么，武力展示？","id":260,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"2","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"武力展示又不是叫你表演杂技......！","id":262,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":263},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"教官，抓好了！","id":265,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"2","id":266},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"——呕吐袋在哪？！","id":268,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialog","id":269},{"type":"Character","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"coverall","id":272},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"仪器已经完全启动！阿米娅，车队可以行动了！","id":275},{"type":"Dialog","id":276},{"type":"Character","id":277},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"好的！","id":280,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"各载具驾驶员，保持匀速！依照图示，利用沙尘的掩蔽接近核心城至可使用登城工具的距离！立刻行动！","id":282,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":283},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_7_9","x":"-100","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","id":284},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"-100","xTo":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","duration":"60","block":"false","id":285},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"playsound","key":"$sportscarstart","volume":"1","id":287},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":288},{"type":"playsound","key":"$sportscarstart","volume":"1","id":289},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":290},{"type":"playsound","key":"$drift","volume":"1","id":291},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":292},{"type":"playsound","key":"$drift","volume":"1","id":293},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":294},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"沙尘掩盖住了我们载具的踪迹，记得戴好防护用具，别让沙尘进入精密器械！","id":296,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但......阳光好清澈啊，为什么阳光能穿透沙尘？","id":297,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"核心城底部的可见度似乎增加了，简直是......法术。","id":298,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们没有......没有这个安排吧？是自然光吧？","id":299,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":300},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......先别管这么多了！","id":302,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"明白！牵引装置，准备发射！各干员，优先确定滑索是否已经完全固定在核心城底部的墙面上！","id":304,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"所有干员都完成转移后，载具会立刻驶走！尽管我很少这么说，但各位干员，我想，现在的阳光，是我们会走好运的兆头！","id":305,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_148_nearl_1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......一定是！","id":307,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"（一不小心让光芒变得太强烈了，只能往地面倾泻这种事我怎么说得出口......）","id":308,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"等等，核心城似乎在加速？","id":309,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"临光","text":"即使整个装置借助了风势，也只能保证沙尘的泼洒涵盖到一公里以内的范围！一旦驶出范围，他们必定会发现我们！","id":310,"figure":"char_148_nearl_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"各位，动作快！","id":312,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"Character","id":313},{"type":"Dialog","id":314},{"type":"playsound","key":"$drift","volume":"1","id":315},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":316},{"type":"playsound","key":"$drift","volume":"1","id":317},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":318},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"image","id":320},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"coverall","id":321},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"playsound","key":"$drift","volume":"1","id":323},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":324},{"type":"playsound","key":"$drift","volume":"1","id":325},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":326},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"来不及了！我们必须立刻减速！","id":328,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"一旦驶出扬尘的范围，切尔诺伯格核心城的光学观察装置可能会立刻捕捉到我们，潜入行动会因此失败！","id":329,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"无论你们还剩几个队员，都快......","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"332","text":"已经不剩下队员了。"}],"values":[],"id":331},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":332},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"欸？","id":334,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"336","text":"我自己来！"},{"id":"336","text":"（默默戴上防尘面具）"},{"id":"336","text":"请将搭扣给我，我一个人上去。"}],"values":[],"id":335},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":336},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":337},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"......太危险了，博士！","id":338,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"没有经过干员训练的人独自登城，简直离谱！","id":339,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驾驶员","text":"凯尔希医生居然没有给你安排战场辅助人员吗？","id":340,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"342","text":"没有就没有，还能怎么样呢？"},{"id":"342","text":"......"},{"id":"342","text":"也许想锻炼我的身体素质才刻意没安排。"}],"values":[],"id":341},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":342},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"有。","id":344,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"346","text":"？！"}],"values":[],"id":345},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":346},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我。","id":348,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":349},{"type":"Character","id":350},{"type":"Text","text":"凯尔希一只手环抱过你的腰部，将你拉上了滑索。","id":351},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"Dr.{@nickname}，下次再自己把握命运吧。","id":353,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":354},{"type":"Character","id":355},{"type":"Background","id":356},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_7_9","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","fadetime":"0","id":358},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"Text","text":"风沙很大，那只“手”很坚硬，你有点不确定它是否属于凯尔希。","id":360},{"type":"Background","id":361},{"type":"Dialog","id":362},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_7_8","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","fadetime":"0","id":364},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"各个小队，请各就各位！","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"接下来的行动，我们不能有任何失误！","id":368},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":369},{"type":"Dialog","id":370},{"type":"Character","id":371},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"image","id":373},{"type":"Background"